import React, {Component} from 'react'
import img5 from './images/pic5.jpg'
import img6 from './images/pic6.jpg'
import img7 from './images/pic7.jpg'
import img8 from './images/pic8.jpg'
import img9 from './images/pic9.jpg'
import img10 from './images/pic10.jpg'
import img11 from './images/pic11.jpg'
import img12 from './images/pic12.jpg'
import img13 from './images/pic13.jpg'
import img14 from './images/pic14.jpg'
import img15 from './images/pic15.jpg'
import img16 from './images/pic16.jpg'
import img17 from './images/pic17.jpg'



const withHOCCounter = WrappedComponent => {
    class WithHOCCounter extends Component {
        constructor(props) {
            super(props)
        
            this.state = {
                arr: [
                    {   img: img5,
                        feature: 'featured',
                        title: 'get together'
                    },
                    {   img: img6,
                        feature: 'simple',
                        title: 'modern business style'
                    },
                    {   img: img7,
                        feature: 'fashion',
                        title: 'memories from last summer'
                    },
                    {   img: img8,
                        feature: 'featured',
                        title: 'lunch time'
                    },
                    {   img: img9,
                        feature: 'day',
                        title: 'amazing day'
                    },
                    {   img: img10,
                        feature: 'fasion',
                        title: 'fitness mantra'
                    },
                    {   img: img11,
                        feature: 'simple',
                        title: 'easter outfit ideas'
                    },
                    {   img: img12,
                        feature: 'featured',
                        title: 'greetings from bottom'
                    },
                    {   img: img13,
                        feature: 'fashion',
                        title: 'say morning'
                    },
                    {   img: img14,
                        feature: 'day',
                        title: 'get together in a fun way'
                    },
                    {   img: img15,
                        feature: 'featured',
                        title: 'follow my steps'
                    },
                    {   img: img16,
                        feature: 'simple',
                        title: 'be cool'
                    },
                    {   img: img17,
                        feature: 'fasion',
                        title: 'new look for new year'
                    }
                ]
            }
            
        }

        render(){
            return <WrappedComponent arr={this.state.arr} />
            
        }
    } 
    return WithHOCCounter
}

export default withHOCCounter
